{"tid":751693,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【聖地牙哥漫畫節】《女超人》宣佈加入首位變性英雄","createTime":"2018-07-22T06:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:20:22.000Z","uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9032e840ed4314b5c4ba37d84aaebd237ccb13ed","tid":751693,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"DC漫畫除咗派出電影亮相聖地牙哥漫畫節，Melissa Benoist主演劇集《女超人》（Supergirl）亦於周六有活動。《女超人》第四季將於10月首播，現場宣佈加入電視史上首個變性英雄人物Dreamer，佢係一心想保護他人嘅年輕跨性別女性，角色會由變性女演員Nicole Maines演出。今季交劇情會交待Nia Nal成為英雄Dreamer嘅旅程，過程有啲似Melissa飾演嘅Kara成為點樣做女超人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180722/large/1532235958_e782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180722%2Flarge%2F1532235958_e782.jpg&h=f4b903bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180722/58472001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F58472001&d=gjMC5PI8QlnGZQbbeUTceWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=59bedaf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F58472001&h=66251cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180722/58472001</a>"},{"pid":"1c771b00c18b27366bccc2a46eadff2e83121e08","tid":751693,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"嗰舊野係碌鳩切唔曬定camel toe黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751e4f55c4db47b79d5b5b0daecbcd7d4e1ae53b","tid":751693,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"幾時出埋vegan man"}]}